short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Wagmi Games AI - Play and Earn $WAGMI rewards

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wagmi Games AI ($WAGMI) is an AI powered blockchain contest platform combined with a gaming and utility $Wagmi token.

This chrome extension adds a Wagmi button to the twitter profiles. Participants of the Twitter hunt contest will be sent trivias in the official Wagmi Games AI Telegram group (https://t.me/wagmigamesai). Once the participants find the answer for the trivia, they have to go to the twitter profile related to the answer and click on the Wagmi button to register their entries. 
Winners will be announced in the Wagmi Games AI Tg.
